<br>
Hell if 99.5% of players wanted rangers to be given Ice Comet what would you see 2 patches down the line? Yep they'd be given Ice Comet, Draughts, and their own version of Lure.<br>
<br>
So sure, say we don't need anything but when druids are given sick spells, none of you can complain cuz we have the oppurtunity to do the same. Things needing to be changed..<br>
<br>
1- ToK turned into either a 25mana, interrupt, 100mana SEIVE (not drain) w/ ~90-120 sec recast, or a balanced silence spell.<br>
<br>
2- Sanctification changed to: if it isn't a mace, sword, axe, or spear you RESIST it ALWAYS. DT, HT, manaburn, ae, nukes, rains, IT DON'T MATTER we should resist every single one and for significantly longer too. <br>
<br>
3-Sup Heal to ~55<br>
<br>
4- Reso along w/ ShoW moved to 58 where Naltron is.<br>
<br>
5- Divine Stun be made worth putting 1, let alone 9, points into.<br>
<br>
6- Brells turned into something better. 200 is mickey mouse. I agree with the hp/ac/svs line. However, just sv magic would be more realistic.<br>
<br>
That should start the list fairly well <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=15242.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=15242.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15242.topic&index=19><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=15242.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.threadControl?topicID=15242.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15242.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15242.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="paladinsofnorrathgeneral">General<option value="paladinsofnorrathfrm14">Norrath Classic and Kunark<option value="paladinsofnorrathfrm15">Velious and Luclin<option value="paladinsofnorrathholyswordsandqu